Package org.usfirst.frc.team2791.robot.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoAim
    Combined command for vision based straightening and shooting
    CalibrateGyro
    Calibrates the Gyro, should be called at robot init.
    DriveEncoderBangBang
    Drives a set distance based on Encoders and power outputs without using PID
    DriveWithJoystick
    Uses the GTADrive I/O Logic to control the Drivetrain.
    EngageRope
    Runs the Climber at a slower speed to catch the rope.
    GearMechDown
    Puts ShakerGear Mechanism down and stops the gear motors from running.
    This will work regardless of the status of the limit switches
    GearMechDownRunMotors
    Puts ShakerGear Mechanism down and starts running gear motors.
    This will work regardless of the status of the ir switch
    GearMechUp
    Puts the Gear Intake up and runs the gears for .5 secs
    HopperOn
    Runs the Hopper to feed balls into the shooter
    IntakeGearFromFloor
    Puts the Gear Intake down and runs the motors
    Automatically raises the gear intake if a gear is recieved
    RunClimber
    Runs the Climber and Engages the ratchet to prevent the robot from falling down the rope
    RunGearMotor
    Runs the Gear Intake motors as long as the gear mechanism is down and the switches aren't activated
    This is the default command for the ShakerGear Subsystem
    RunHopper
    Runs the ShakerHopper motors backwards, can be used to unjam the hopper
    RunHopperBackwards
    Runs the ShakerHopper motors backwards, can be used to unjam the hopper
    RunIntake
    Runs the ShakerIntake motors and actuates the intake to the outward position
    RunLongShot
    Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    RunLongShotWithMetering
    Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    RunVisionShot
    Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    RunVisionShotWithTable
    !!!!sPLS DO NOT USE OR INSTANTIATE!!!! Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    RunWallShot
    Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    RunWallShotWithMetering
    Simultanesouly runs the ShakerShooter and ShakerHopper.
    ScoreGearAutoReturn
    Puts ShakerGear Mechanism down and stops the gear motors from running.
    This will work regardless of the status of the limit switches
    SpinUpShooter  
    TurnGyroBangBang  
    WaitForGearSwitches
    Puts the Gear Intake up if it is already down and it has a gear according to the limit switch
    This is the default command for the ShakerGear Subsystem
